{
  "abstract": "Government of Karnataka has taken a novel initiative viz; SurvarnaBhoomiYojane (SBY) to\r\nhelp the small and marginal farmers to shift from growing low-value crops to high-value\r\ncrops by providing Rs. 10,000/- cash incentive directly into their bank accounts for\r\ndeveloping two acres of land. The Department of Horticulture, Government of Karnataka\r\nhas supported ICRISAT to provide technical support to SuvarnaBhoomiYojaneHorticulture\r\n(SBY-H) beneficiaries totalling 0.25 million in 30 districts...",
